ows\nbackend/src/infra/runtime/dummy_runner.py-7-exercise both verification and retry/terminal paths.\nbackend/src/infra/runtime/dummy_runner.py-8-\nbackend/src/infra/runtime/dummy_runner.py-9-The implementation lives in src/app/testing/fakes.py (the application layer may\nbackend/src/infra/runtime/dummy_runner.py-10-not import infra, so the sharing points this way); this module is the infra\n--\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-4-  PROJECT_REPO_DIR      target repo for the git-branching workspace\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-5-                        (defaults to <orchestrator_home>/workspace-repo)\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-6-\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-7-Neither the REASONER nor the AGENT RUNNER is env-selected — both resolve from\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-8-SQLite:\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-9-  reasoner       config key reasoner.mode (stub|llm) + the providers catalog +\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-10-                 the envelope-encrypted secret store\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-11-                 (src/infra/reasoner/factory.py).\nbackend/src/infra/container.py:12:  agent_runner   config key agent_runner.mode (dry-run|real); in real mode\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-13-                 each task resolves through the AGENT REGISTRY — the bound\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-14-                 AgentSpec's runtime_type + provider/model catalog rows\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-15-                 (src/infra/runtime/factory.py).\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-16-\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-17-Environment is read ONLY here (the composition root) — never deep in the code.\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-18-\"\"\"\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-19-\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-20-from __future__ import annotations\n--\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-43-from src.infra.db.chat_repository import SqliteChatRepository\nbackend/src/infra/container.py-44-from src.infra.db.secret_store import SqliteSecretStore, load_master_key